These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
House: colonial, craftsman, art-deco, cottage
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, engineer, social-worker, accountant
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, van, skateboard, airplane
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, almond-milk, milk
 1. the police-officer is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 3. the cottage house is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the colonial house##1
 9. the social-worker is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the engineer##1
11. the colonial house is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| House         | cottage    | art-deco   | colonial | craftsman      |
| Job   | engineer       | police-officer | social-worker     | accountant    |
| Transport   | airplane | van         | snowmobile  | skateboard    |
| Beverage           | almond-milk      | milk       | water | soy-milk |

