.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, old-henry, dunhill, ritmeester
City: paris, berlin, london, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, azure, purple, blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, scooter, jet-ski, taxi
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 8. the person who likes azure is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person traveling to london is the fan of indie##1
10. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
11. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Cigar      | old-henry      | fonseca     | dunhill    | ritmeester |
| City   | paris | berlin   | london   | marseilles           |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b     | indie    | disco         |
| Color           | blue         | azure | purple     | aquamarine        |
| Transport         | car     | taxi  | scooter | jet-ski       |

