.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, may, september
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, musician, photographer, librarian
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, writing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, tennis, weightlifting
House: wooden, townhouse, gothic-revival, farmhouse
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the farmhouse house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the photographer is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 8. the wooden house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the librarian is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the musician is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Birthday          | april    | september      | may  | february   |
| Job   | librarian     | photographer      | musician | teacher      |
| Hobby           | hiking       | collecting         | gardening  | writing         |
| Sport         | basketball | snowboarding | tennis  | weightlifting |
| House     | gothic-revival       | wooden         | farmhouse   | townhouse        |

