 1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of electronic is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is the fan of rock##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 7. the cain-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes orange is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
11. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the rabbit##1
12. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Pet      | rabbit     | pony      | chinchilla    | fish           |
