 1. the indonesian is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the baccarat-smoker##1
 3. the egyptian is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person traveling to boston is the chinese##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| City    | hannover     | london  | boston       | hamburg      |
| Hobby       | singing    | writing        | collecting  | drawing      |
| Cigar         | dunhill  | bongani | baccarat | havana |
| Nationality         | egyptian | malaysian          | chinese         | indonesian      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | fantasy     | documentary       | epic          |

