.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, red, coral, fuchsia
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, begonia, amaryllis, iris
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, scientist, manager, freelancer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, march, may
 1. the manager is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the freelancer is on the left of the project-manager##1
 5. the person who likes coral is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| Color         | fuchsia | coral | red | azure  |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | begonia     | iris      | tulip |
| Job   | manager  | freelancer     | project-manager    | scientist  |
| Birthday           | january  | may       | august          | march      |

