.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, plum, raspberry, tomato
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, tulip, bellflower
4 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, fish, snake
House: art-deco, tower, futuristic, modern
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, chaman, swisher, montecristo
