 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the swisher-smoker is the person who growstulip##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 8. the modern house is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the modern house is the person eating raspberry##1
11. the art-deco house is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
12. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
