City: london, miami, berlin, nizza
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, turkish, nigerian, russian
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, goldfish, snake
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, fanta, water
 1. the russian is the person traveling to london##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the russian is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the australian##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the turkish##1
 8. the australian is the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the person who likes coral is the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Color        | blue    | coral        | orange        | fuchsia      |
| City       | berlin       | london       | miami      | nizza |
| Nationality         | turkish | russian | nigerian | australian      |
| Pet         | cat          | snake         | goat           | goldfish    |
| Beverage   | fanta         | tea       | water     | milk   |

 